Provo UT 84604
NOTICE OF LIEN
RODNEY D. CAMPBELL
NT 103479:2009 P6 1 of 1
UTAH COUNTY RECORDER
2009 Sep 28 4:34 pm FEE 10.00 BY SS
RECORDED FOR TPM
TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN:
NOTICE IS HEREBY GIVEN that The Cedars Townhomes hereby claims and intends to hold a lien
upon certain land and premises owned or reputed to be owned by Brandon & Tavah Babcock located
at 3824 West Morgan Blvd ., Cedar Hills, UT, 84062, and which is legalally described as:
Lot 136 , Plat E , The Cedars Townhomes PRD .
Drake
Sub. arca 0.04 AC
This lien is to secure the payment of 508.86 owing to The Cedars Townhomes as assessment against said
real property.
Said indebtedness represents the expenses assessed against the owner in accordance with the
Homeowners Bylaws, the terms of which the undersigned did hereby agree to abide.
The undersigned holds and claims lien against said real property by virture of the provisions of Section
20, Chapter 8, Title 57, Utah Code Ann. [1953 as amended], and by virtue of the declaration of the
property referred to above.
Dated this 9/28/2009
The Cedars Townhomes
By: dec2
Angela Cook, Assisstant HOA Manager
Subscribed and sworn before me this
28 day of Soet , 2009.
State of UTAH
County of UTAH
Notary Public
LANELL STEWART
2200 N. University Parkway Suite 74!
Provo. Utah 84604
